{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had two other cousins who were more or less in the age bracket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, and I was pretty young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yes, the family would do a lot of the things like I described.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like when we went skiing and we went to these vacations, the family was very-- it seemed to me we would often go together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, rent a villa for the family rather than just for our parents and my sister and me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There would be like, you know, 12 people there, 14 people, and-- and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in that kind of a world, you had no sense of anti-Semitism?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you even understand that Jews were different than the Catholics?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or how did that--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--I didn't, because I was protected from it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- you know, we were not living in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember on one or two occasions-- maybe there were more, I don't remember that-- but I remember going to visit poorer relatives who lived either in the ghetto or who lived and dressed the way one associates with Orthodox Jews prior to World War II.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My grandfather had a beard and looked like that, but it was still within the context of a wealthy family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember feeling the difference, like going into their apartment and could smell the cooking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was kind of cramped and closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Living with my mother's family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's family came from Lwow, Lemberg, I believe it's also called.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew about them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had an interesting history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, some of his brothers had come to America in the 1920s and actually worked briefly in films, which is interesting because here I am today living in Los Angeles [LAUGHS] and working in films.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
